Mainly its going to be for administration
    Top contributors (users with most ideas)
    Most popular tags
    Most active domains
    Recent idea activity trends (last N days)
    Most liked ideas


Data fetching
    Aggregations from MySQL (for users, tags, idea count)
    Aggregations from MongoDB (likes, comments count)
    Time-based trends (e.g., ideas per day)
    Domain distribution